# Environment variable templates
#
# This repository uses separate environment files for each client interface.
# Copy the appropriate file for your use case and fill your values:
#
#   Console:       cp .env.console.example .env.console
#   FastAPI server: cp .env.api.example .env.api
#   M365 adapter:  cp .env.m365.example .env.m365
#
# See the package-specific example files for the full list of variables.
